 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6635819ed33e89778562cda0e40dafe2ab5fa14f","tid":2000602,"uid":113277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:20:16.000Z","msg":"關你 l 事咩，黃店做唔住咪最大懲罰囉。家陣人地做得到，你吹咩？自由經濟之下，點樣做生意要你管？"},{"pid":"e258ad075e22cb1f1571426e2722ef71dbc23a4f","tid":2000602,"uid":114781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:20:17.000Z","msg":"支那狗真係好撚驚黃色經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"890828ecf5c0b79c88639218c02e03b1e1e304ab","tid":2000602,"uid":66898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdcb5ae026a1ec6806d56ed0006f4ec997dbe26e","tid":2000602,"uid":220766,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T03:49:22.000Z","msg":"係客揀店 邊黎店揀客"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:20:35.000Z","msg":"大陸未來好似有 雖然評論黎<br />\nSource:<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1587732513627&amp;issue=20200424\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1587732513627%26issue%3D20200424&d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWX29V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=39b993ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1587732513627%26issue%3D20200424&h=5f1344a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1587732513627&amp;issue=20200424</a><br />\nDCEP即是Digital Currency Electronic Payment，是由中國人民銀行發行、具有價值特徵及流通現金（M0）屬性的數碼支付工具。由於人行發行的DCEP，DCEP與人民幣有相同法定地位，相當於電子版人民幣，除了具有法律補償性外，規定任何中國機構及14億人民不能拒絕DCEP。<br />\n<br />\nDCEP功能有五，分別是<br />\n1）降低發行現鈔的成本及打擊假鈔問題、<br />\n2）人行更靈活地控制貨幣供應、控制銀行貸款及直接融資、<br />\n3）推出非常規貨幣政策、<br />\n4）限制資金流失及洗黑錢、<br />\n5）阻止貪污囤積巨鈔問題。<br />\n先講講非常規貨幣政策，簡而言之，即是人行可以針對經濟表現欠佳的地區推出短期負利率措施，達到即時刺激經濟的目的。<br />\n<br />\n除了推出短期負利率等非常規措施，更極端的措施可以限制DCEP作某特定用途，例如向市民額外<span style=\"color: red;\">發放1,000元人民幣資金</span>，但資金只<span style=\"color: red;\">能用作購買受限制糧食</span>之用，變相達到上世紀計劃經濟時中國居民供應票證的目的。<br />\n<br />\n全文去返日月報條link<br />\n<br />\n其實唔一定指定用途 重可以指定商店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8689c87a670cfc4f39bf72702e75074b76a9b43","tid":2000602,"uid":136973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:20:40.000Z","msg":"當呢啲文去到每日10篇，就知道藍店真係死到臨頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc45df710f26ec2a6dd0013919f7866ddd19fe1a","tid":2000602,"uid":283130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:20:47.000Z","msg":"難有作為但日日都要鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f26472c07d962bc9c60624abe7e35ebeaae5532","tid":2000602,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:20:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢一兩個月啲紅媒出咗幾撚多篇文講"},{"pid":"92c485d65d21a6dc1bc18a34587b6ff4992a3d1b","tid":2000602,"uid":288304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:22:06.000Z","msg":"係ga, 自尋死路, 咁畀佢哋執晒, 到時咪你賺晒lol"},{"pid":"222c2d1c3165b0f3debac12524848be97a335b34","tid":2000602,"uid":304769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:22:10.000Z","msg":"關於黃色經濟圈，我有d野想講：<br />\n<br />\n我想講翻其實黃色經濟圈最核心精神係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>紅死藍貧，紅死是為了打擊支共呢個恐怖份子籌集資金。藍唔洗死，但要慘比其他綠絲睇，就係為左&ldquo;統戰&rdquo;綠絲，壯大黃色經濟圈。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n所以大家幫襯黃店之外亦要記得先紅後藍：<br />\n<br />\n1.切斷中國國企在香港經營獲得外匯收入的機會，以加速支爆。<br />\n2.令藍絲企業經營困難，&ldquo;統戰&rdquo;綠絲企業<br />\n舉例，呢個原則點樣用：<br />\n基於先紅後藍原則，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">銀行方面一定係先中銀後匯豐</span></strong><br />\n根據先紅後藍原則，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">應該先Pacific(華潤)後Starbucks（美心）</span></strong><br />\n基於先紅後藍原則，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>&ldquo;幫襯&rdquo;紅店力度不應該比藍店細。尤其各種隱性紅店係支共既重要回血劍</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"104a857631417baa3c4d7ae51dd7bc5fac5b5934","tid":2000602,"uid":7270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:23:03.000Z","msg":"大公/文匯：好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n藍店中資同志<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無飯開<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n樓主pin this please<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5276935accd5e215a759800095d5cdafa4573a13","tid":2000602,"uid":140949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:23:08.000Z","msg":"我食果啲黃店都好食喎，唔知佢老作啲咩，成篇嘢都無logic,同共狗一樣"},{"pid":"13329980a8f0de8e95e84f75611d5521f9592ba1","tid":2000602,"uid":126382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f26472c07d962bc9c60624abe7e35ebeaae5532","tid":2000602,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:20:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢一兩個月啲紅媒出咗幾撚多篇文講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:23:25.000Z","msg":"一路話黃店就玩完，但愈出愈多文，咩玩法嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces